        public void publish(java.lang.String fN,
           java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> extHdr,
           java.lang.String msg,
           java.util.List<ContentBlock> cBlocks,
           java.lang.String dsSig)
        Wraps up a list of content blocks as a TAXII message and publishes them to the flare TAXII server
        Parameters:
        fN - feed name
        extHdr - a HashMap containing all extended headers (can be null)
        msg - string containing optional "Message" element (can be null)
        cBlocks - list of ContentBlock objects, each containing an individual content block for the TAXII message
        dsSig - string containing the digital signature for the TAXII message (can be null)
